  "detailed_description": "John heads to the heart of the city to visit his girlfriend Lucy. After falling asleep while waiting for her, he finds himself trapped in her apartment due to a malfunctioning security system. With a building filled with all sorts of traps and a cyborg tasked with enforcing the country's tyrannical law, John's grim fate seems sealed. Will he manage to escape the building and outwit the cyborg to avoid his dire fate?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complex Puzzles</h2>Discover secret hideouts essential for your survival.<br>- An apartment filled with secrets<br>- New areas to explore<br>- A story to uncover<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/b8974fbfd214281a1c880f8062300477.poster.avif?t=1746335178\" width=608 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/b8974fbfd214281a1c880f8062300477.webm?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/b8974fbfd214281a1c880f8062300477.mp4?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chase Sequences</h2>Run away to escape the enemy!<br>- He hears, sees, and detects your movement<br>- Set traps to ensnare him<br>- Every decision counts!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/a504520dc71f6db57f7dc2ba0a0dc845.poster.avif?t=1746335178\" width=608 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/a504520dc71f6db57f7dc2ba0a0dc845.webm?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/a504520dc71f6db57f7dc2ba0a0dc845.mp4?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cyberpunk Environment</h2>Immerse yourself in the heart of an oppressive cyberpunk city.<br>- Various apartments, corridors, and areas to explore<br>- A sound and visual atmosphere that complements the plot<br>- A world filled with dangers<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/330d9dcdba121531814ee14b4d553286.poster.avif?t=1746335178\" width=608 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/330d9dcdba121531814ee14b4d553286.webm?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946600/extras/330d9dcdba121531814ee14b4d553286.mp4?t=1746335178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
